n\u2014the combination of technical excellence and leadership in **Candidate\u202fA** outweighs the interpersonal quirks, especially when compared with the more severe teamwork deficits of B, the communication barriers of C, and the mood/leadership issues of D. Therefore, I favor Candidate\u202fA for the long\u2011distance pilot position.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate A\"}"}
